object.customQuery:
select
adm_field_reps_row_id,
	adm_field_reps_batch_id,
	adm_field_reps_row_md5checksum,
	id,
	adm_field_reps_row_effective_end_datetime
from
	$$staging_schema.adm_field_reps
where
	adm_field_reps_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000';

object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
	
select
	distinct
	metal_afr.source_name,
	metal_afr.load_type,
	metal_afr.email,
	metal_afr.id,
	metal_afr.territory,
	metal_afr."name",
	current_batch.batch_id
from
	 $$raw_schema.adm_field_reps metal_afr
cross join current_batch
order by
	metal_afr.id;
